============================================================

Concept:     Transfer Learning
Category:    Technique
Definition:  Reuses pre-trained model weights for new related tasks
Year:        2009
Researchers: Pan and Yang survey
Applications:Fine-tuning LLMs, computer vision
Related:     Pre-training, fine-tuning, domain adaptation

Concept:     Hallucination
Category:    Problem
Definition:  LLM confidently generates plausible but incorrect information
Year:        2020
Researchers: Many researchers
Applications:AI reliability, factual QA systems
Related:     Retrieval augmentation, grounding, calibration

Concept:     Attention Mechanism
Category:    Mechanism
Definition:  Learns to focus on relevant input parts for each output
Year:        2015
Researchers: Bahdanau et al.
Applications:Machine translation, NLP, summarization
Related:     Self-attention, multi-head, cross-attention

